creator: Visionary Labs
descriptionHtml:
CreditLog: Udhar Khata Book, Ledger Account app will replace your traditional Udhar Khata notes by new Digital ledger Account book.

It is completely safe and secure for every businesses to maintain their customers' ledger accounts.

* Secure your CreditLog: Udhar Khata Book, Ledger Account using App Lock
Useful for every personal/business to record credit (Jama) and debit (Udhar) transactions for their Customers.

CreditLog: Udhar Khata Book, Ledger Account App Features :
- You can use for it for as Personal and Business account
- Easy Backup & restore Khata Book data
- Share PDF file of your ledger account to your customer.
- Set type Personal/Business and currency
- Date time formatting, cloud backup restore features
- Easy to clear all transaction records
- Excellent PDF format of customer transactions, Easy to share
- Edit/Delete old transactions of your ledgers entries
- Delete Transaction from your account book
- Manage multiple shops within one app
- Udhar Khata Book, Ledger Account Book
- My Cash Book, Mobile Ledger, Pocket ledger
- Account Book, Pocket Account, Khatavahi Hisab Book
